  "detailed_description": "In this captivating Metroidvania game you will take on the role of a cute kitty on its mission to find the soul of Planet 42 to rescue the Earth. Fight enemies and bosses, solve puzzles and explore levels in this fascinating game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/608a96a702f931d40174dd890a9ada25.poster.avif?t=1705263001\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/608a96a702f931d40174dd890a9ada25.webm?t=1705263001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/608a96a702f931d40174dd890a9ada25.mp4?t=1705263001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>Along the way you will meet different characters, each with their own story to tell, and by the end you will be faced with a difficult moral choice<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/c9af398bb903de2ea3ebda857a8f9356.poster.avif?t=1705263001\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/c9af398bb903de2ea3ebda857a8f9356.webm?t=1705263001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/c9af398bb903de2ea3ebda857a8f9356.mp4?t=1705263001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>What's inside:<br>• 19 unique enemies<br>• 6 large biome maps to explore<br>• 6 challenging bosses<br>• 7 types of weapons <br>• various quests<br>• more than 10 characters, each with their own story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/97453e0c57bd0f3ea799cb72ec52d1d0.poster.avif?t=1705263001\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/97453e0c57bd0f3ea799cb72ec52d1d0.webm?t=1705263001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2072970/extras/97453e0c57bd0f3ea799cb72ec52d1d0.mp4?t=1705263001\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.",
